That's not it at all!\""},

{"lineNumber":119378,"originalJapaneseLine":"「不健全……なんて不健全な……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Unwholesome... what unwholesomeness...\""},

{"lineNumber":119379,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ううーむ、これも性の乱れの一つって奴か……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, is this also one of those sexual disorders...\""},

{"lineNumber":119380,"originalJapaneseLine":"　閉鎖的な環境に男一人、女八人で","translatedEnglishLine":"\"One man and eight women living in a closed environment...\""},

{"lineNumber":119381,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ずーっと暮らしてるとそんなもんかもな……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Maybe it's natural for something like that to happen over time...\""},

{"lineNumber":119382,"originalJapaneseLine":"「しかし、なんと不健全な……うぅーむ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"However, how utterly unwholesome... hmm...\""},

{"lineNumber":119383,"originalJapaneseLine":"「だだだ、だからあたしは違うって――！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I-I-I'm telling you, I'm not like that――!\""},

{"lineNumber":119384,"originalJapaneseLine":"「由々しき問題だ……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"This is a serious problem...\""},

{"lineNumber":119385,"originalJapaneseLine":"　城の女の子達には注意喚起しておかんと……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"I have to warn the girls in the castle...\""},

{"lineNumber":119386,"originalJapaneseLine":"　バイならまだいいがレズはいかんぞぉ……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Being bisexual is one thing, but lesbians? That's not okay...\""},

{"lineNumber":119387,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスはぶつぶつと深刻そうな顔をして、","translatedEnglishLine":"Lance muttered with a serious expression,"},

{"lineNumber":119388,"originalJapaneseLine":"温泉から出ていった。","translatedEnglishLine":"and left the hot spring."},

{"lineNumber":119389,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\""},

{"lineNumber":119390,"originalJapaneseLine":"「な、な、な……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"W-W-What...\" "},

{"lineNumber":119391,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんっっだ、あいつはーーー！」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What the hell is with that guyーーー!\" "},

{"lineNumber":119392,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あらあら〜、捕まっちゃいましたね〜」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh my, looks like you got caught~\" "},

{"lineNumber":119393,"originalJapaneseLine":"「おや？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119394,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あ、ランス様」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ah, Lord Lance.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119395,"originalJapaneseLine":"「こんにちは、ランスさん」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hello, Lance.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119396,"originalJapaneseLine":"ランスが加奈代の部屋に遊びに行くと、","translatedEnglishLine":"When Lance visited Kanayo's room,"},

{"lineNumber":119397,"originalJapaneseLine":"先にシィルがいた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Cyll was there first."},

{"lineNumber":119398,"originalJapaneseLine":"「なんだ、いつの間に仲良くなったんだ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"What, since when did you two become so close?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119399,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ちょっと前からですね〜。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"It's been a little while now~."},

{"lineNumber":119400,"originalJapaneseLine":"　この城に来るにあたって、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"When I came to this castle,"},

{"lineNumber":119401,"originalJapaneseLine":"　シィルちゃんには色々とよくして頂いてたので〜」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Cyll has been very kind to me~\" "},

{"lineNumber":119402,"originalJapaneseLine":"「それに……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"And besides...\" "},

{"lineNumber":119403,"originalJapaneseLine":"「シィルちゃん、可愛いから、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Cyll is so cute,"},

{"lineNumber":119404,"originalJapaneseLine":"　私がすっかり気に入ってしまって」","translatedEnglishLine":"I've completely taken a liking to her.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119405,"originalJapaneseLine":"「はあ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119406,"originalJapaneseLine":"「そうかぁ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Is that so?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119407,"originalJapaneseLine":"「くすん……ひどい……」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Sniff... that's mean...\" "},

{"lineNumber":119408,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うふふ、可愛いですよ〜」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ufufu, you are cute~\" "},

{"lineNumber":119409,"originalJapaneseLine":"「性格も見た目もとっても可愛い」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Your personality and appearance are both very cute.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119410,"originalJapaneseLine":"「あう……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Auu... "},

{"lineNumber":119411,"originalJapaneseLine":"　て、照れちゃいます……」","translatedEnglishLine":"I'm blushing...\" "},

{"lineNumber":119412,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ふーん、よく分からん」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Hmm, I don't quite get it.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119413,"originalJapaneseLine":"「少し……","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Maybe... "},

{"lineNumber":119414,"originalJapaneseLine":"　気をつけた方がいいかも」","translatedEnglishLine":"It's better to be careful.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119415,"originalJapaneseLine":"「お、なんだ、ちびメイドコンビ。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Oh, what is this, the little maid duo."},

{"lineNumber":119416,"originalJapaneseLine":"　気をつけた方が、ってのは」","translatedEnglishLine":"What do you mean by 'better to be careful'?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119417,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うーん、加奈代さんは、なんていうかぁ」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well, Kanayo-san is, how should I say,"},

{"lineNumber":119418,"originalJapaneseLine":"「女性の方が好きなんです」","translatedEnglishLine":"someone who prefers women.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119419,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ん？　なんのこっちゃ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Huh? What's that about?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119420,"originalJapaneseLine":"「言葉通りですよー。","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Just as it sounds—"},

{"lineNumber":119421,"originalJapaneseLine":"　男性よりも女性の方が好き、なんです」","translatedEnglishLine":"she likes women more than men.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119422,"originalJapaneseLine":"「…………」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"........\" "},

{"lineNumber":119423,"originalJapaneseLine":"「え、レズ？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Eh, lesbian?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119424,"originalJapaneseLine":"リリムはそっと頷いた。","translatedEnglishLine":"Lilim nodded quietly."},

{"lineNumber":119425,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ええっ！？」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ehh!?\" "},

{"lineNumber":119426,"originalJapaneseLine":"「うふふ〜、だって女の子の方が、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Ufufu~ because girls are,"},

{"lineNumber":119427,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ふわふわ柔らかくていいじゃないですか〜♪」","translatedEnglishLine":"soft and fluffy and so nice~♪\" "},

{"lineNumber":119428,"originalJapaneseLine":"「ま、相手の許可なく襲うようなことは、","translatedEnglishLine":"\"Well, I would never attack anyone without their permission,"},

{"lineNumber":119429,"originalJapaneseLine":"　ぜーったいにしないので安心して下さい」","translatedEnglishLine":"so please don't worry.\" "},

{"lineNumber":119430,"originalJapaneseLine":"「君、シィルに近づくの禁止」","translatedEnglishLine":"\"You are forbidden to get close to Cyll.\""}]}

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ぎゃああああああああ！」
ななな、何入ってきてんの！」
「はあ、な、なによ！？」
「なんか色々と名前が出て来たが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "A bunch of names have come up but..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ケッセルメイドって、そういう関係なのか？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Kessel Maids, you mean they have that kind of relationship?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ち、ちがっ！　あたしは全然、そんなんじゃ！」
「不健全……なんて不健全な……」
「ううーむ、これも性の乱れの一つって奴か……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Hmm, is this also one of those sexual disorders..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 閉鎖的な環境に男一人、女八人で
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "One man and eight women living in a closed environment..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ずーっと暮らしてるとそんなもんかもな……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Maybe it's natural for something like that to happen over time..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「しかし、なんと不健全な……うぅーむ……」
「だだだ、だからあたしは違うって――！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I-I-I'm telling you, I'm not like that――!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「由々しき問題だ……
城の女の子達には注意喚起しておかんと……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "I have to warn the girls in the castle..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: バイならまだいいがレズはいかんぞぉ……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Being bisexual is one thing, but lesbians? That's not okay..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスはぶつぶつと深刻そうな顔をして、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance muttered with a serious expression,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 温泉から出ていった。
「なんっっだ、あいつはーーー！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What the hell is with that guyーーー!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あらあら〜、捕まっちゃいましたね〜」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh my, looks like you got caught~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「おや？」
「あ、ランス様」
「こんにちは、ランスさん」
ランスが加奈代の部屋に遊びに行くと、
先にシィルがいた。
「なんだ、いつの間に仲良くなったんだ？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "What, since when did you two become so close?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ちょっと前からですね〜。
この城に来るにあたって、
シィルちゃんには色々とよくして頂いてたので〜」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Cyll has been very kind to me~"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「それに……」
「シィルちゃん、可愛いから、
私がすっかり気に入ってしまって」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I've completely taken a liking to her."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「はあ？」
「そうかぁ？」
「くすん……ひどい……」
「うふふ、可愛いですよ〜」
「性格も見た目もとっても可愛い」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Your personality and appearance are both very cute."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あう……
て、照れちゃいます……」
「ふーん、よく分からん」
「少し……
気をつけた方がいいかも」
「お、なんだ、ちびメイドコンビ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Oh, what is this, the little maid duo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 気をつけた方が、ってのは」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: What do you mean by 'better to be careful'?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うーん、加奈代さんは、なんていうかぁ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, Kanayo-san is, how should I say,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「女性の方が好きなんです」
「ん？　なんのこっちゃ？」
「言葉通りですよー。
男性よりも女性の方が好き、なんです」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: she likes women more than men."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「え、レズ？」
リリムはそっと頷いた。
「ええっ！？」
「うふふ〜、だって女の子の方が、
ふわふわ柔らかくていいじゃないですか〜♪」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: soft and fluffy and so nice~♪"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、相手の許可なく襲うようなことは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, I would never attack anyone without their permission,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぜーったいにしないので安心して下さい」
「君、シィルに近づくの禁止」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You are forbidden to get close to Cyll."
